author: William A.
title: Spokane, Washington GOP offices vandalized.
text:
Spokane, Washington GOP offices vandalized. Posted at 5:40   William A.   
Overnight Saturday in Spokane, Washington: #Spokane GOP office targeted by vandals Sunday, according to Spokane Co. Party Chairman Stephanie Cates (Photo: Spokane GOP) pic.twitter.com/XbxjOtiVMa 
— KREM 2 NEWS (@KREM2) January 29, 2017 Spokane GOP's office was vandalized overnight. They've reported it to police @KHQLocalNews pic.twitter.com/vMCOVpwpcm 
— Katie Chen (@KHQKatieChen) January 29, 2017 Just spoke with Spokane Co. GOP chair, Stephanie Cates, who says their focus is on positivity @KHQLocalNews pic.twitter.com/mFagk81xNX 
— Katie Chen (@KHQKatieChen) January 29, 2017 Office of @SpokaneGOP & @cathymcmorris hit by vandals. GOP calls it retaliation for Trump's order re: #refugees . (1/2) pic.twitter.com/fJgLPr9UWZ 
— Melissa Luck ☘ (@MelissaKXLY4) January 29, 2017 We have heard a troubling report that the Spokane GOP headquarters have been vandalized. The Spokane County… https://t.co/DPGEL2ns4M 
— Spokane Democrats (@SpokaneDemParty) January 29, 2017 In response to vandalism of @SpokaneGOP & @cathymcmorris office, GOP chair says politically motivated crimes should be "hate crimes." #kxly pic.twitter.com/JZVhDFeEFw 
— Melissa Luck ☘ (@MelissaKXLY4) January 29, 2017 @MelissaKXLY4 @SpokaneGOP @cathymcmorris nope. @GOP is guilty of hate crimes. Windows can be washed.
